        </param>
        <param>
          <type>size_t</type>
          <declname>n</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Compares two (16-bit) Unicode strings. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>s1</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>a pointer to the first string. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>s2</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>a pointer to the second string. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>n</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>the maximum number of characters to compare.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>an integer greater than, equal to, or less than 0 if the string at <bold>s1</bold> is greater than, equal to, or less than the string at <bold>s2</bold>. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
